The freetype-py source code is obtained from
http://freetype-py.googlecode.com/files/freetype-py-0.4.1.tar.gz
and is licensed under the revised BSD license

This Makefile can be used to install Python bindings for the freetype
library.

To install, execute the following in this directory::

  make

and then, with superuser permissions:

   make install

